oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Put 'Em Up!
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of two men engaging in a boxing match in front of the Old Globe Store in Wilson Hill, Tennessee. Roy Davis is the man on the left. Another man is watching from the porch of the store. Wili Bobo is standing on the far right next to the horse-and-buggy.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Boxing; Stores & shops; Carriages & coaches
